                    NUTRITION
                </h2>
            <p class="paragh"> 
                Nutrition plays a key role in maintaining a healthy body and mind. It refers to the food we eat and how it affects our growth, energy, and overall health. A balanced diet includes proteins, carbohydrates, healthy fats, vitamins, and minerals. These nutrients help the body function properly, build muscles, and support the immune system. Good nutrition also improves concentration, mood, and physical performance. Drinking enough water and avoiding too much sugar, fast food, and processed meals are important for staying healthy. Eating fresh fruits and vegetables daily helps the body get natural vitamins and antioxidants. In short, proper nutrition is the foundation of a strong and healthy lifestyle.
